      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in truly impeccable condition. This specimen has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, resulting in a finish and mechanical state that mirror its original delivery. The exterior retains a deep, showroom-level luster, while the interior remains pristine and free of any discernible wear. Rigorously inspected and verified for peak performance, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and an authoritative presence on the road.",
      "price": 43900.0,
