      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total gem! This car is in pristine, mint condition\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and honestly looks like it just left the showroom. Not a scratch in sight and the interior feels brand new! It drives incredibly smooth and is 100% ready for a new home. I'm looking for someone who will appreciate just how well-maintained this beauty is. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
