    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E36 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the S52 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear torque through a precise ZF 5-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe is free of stress fractures. The factory-spec limited-slip differential provides exceptional turn-out traction, complemented by an M-Technic suspension that remains taut and responsive. Retaining all original factory VIN tags, the chassis shows zero signs of oxidative stress or hydraulic leaks. Finished with a pristine 'Vader' interior, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
